ActCanadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety Act
PrecisAppointment of KIMBERLY DUNPHY of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, to be a governor of the Council of the Canadian Centre for Occupational Health and Safety being the nominee of the Lieutenant Governor in Council of the Province of Newfoundland and Labrador to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years.
